nodes.text: The Insider Online Supplement was an exclusive feature on the Star Wars fan club website, Star Wars Hyperspace. It provided additional background and content related to articles published in the Star Wars Insider magazine. Articles covered topics on the Star Wars universe, events, fiction, previews, collecting, merchandising, and interviews.

The online supplement was published online for Insider issues 77-99 primarily coinciding with the publishing run under IDG Entertainment. Following the recent redesign of StarWars.com, the Online supplement has been removed and archived issues are no longer available.
